title: Beijing 2022: Tess Coady and Jenise Spiteri on highs and lows of snowboarding
description: The daily podcast contains two snowboarders today. Australia's Tess Coady took a bronze medal in slopestyle - four years after she tore her ACL in a practice session at PyeongChang 2018. And Jenise Spiteri slept in a van without a heater for two winters to make her half pipe Olympic dream come alive. Get ready to be inspired!
